    "Uniques system - text-based game mechanic modifiers with parameters and conditionals",
    "ModOptions.json - mod configuration including isBaseRuleset flag",
    "Translation files in android/assets/jsons/translations/",
    "gradlew desktop:run / desktop:dist - build and run commands",
